thread.title: Siobhan Muldowney
thread.title_full: Mabel's Labels reviewed by Siobhan Muldowney

author: Siobhan Muldowney
title: Siobhan Muldowney
text:
We first got these labels nearly 15 years ago. They really are terrific. They stay on where they're supposed to. So many pairs of boots, shoes retrieved quickly from the pile in front of the door. So many clothing articles returned from the school list and found. I love them!
I've ordered labels as my "Welcome Bsby" gift forever. It's the one gift you know will be used and will still be in use years later.
